      "content": "# billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries\n\n`powerhouse/billing-statement` (7 ops) produces periodic billing summaries. Since [[subscription-instance model tracks active customer subscriptions with lifecycle state]], billing statements likely aggregate subscription charges per billing cycle.\n\n## Cross-Model References\n\n- SubscriptionInstance → BillingStatement (billing cycle outputs)\n- May reference [[accounts model defines the chart of accounts structure]] for account assignment\n- May feed into [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]]\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
